{"TopicId":214111,"ForumId":119,"TopicTitle":"KSP2 dropped its price?","CreatedByName":"Buenasfx","CreatedById":209161,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-01T21:51:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Buenasfx","CreatedById":209161,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-01T21:51:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP2 lowered its price in Mexico from 1,000mxn (50dls) to 564.99mxn (28dls) Did the same happen in other countries? Those of us who bought it for 50dls will get a refund?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MarcAbaddon","CreatedById":192494,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-01T22:35:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo change for me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mutex","CreatedById":106937,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-01T22:35:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you mean on Steam? Still \u00A344.99 in the UK.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-01T23:03:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteamdb shows that it dropped the price on 24th, release day. Probably price was converted but that\u0027s a significant drop, and on day one, assuming it happened some hours after release, is a bit sketchy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Buenasfx","CreatedById":209161,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-01T23:49:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn Steam and also on the official page of Private Division\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jarin","CreatedById":71395,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T00:21:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224249248\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022214111\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677711814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteamdb shows that it dropped the price on 24th, release day. Probably price was converted but that\u0027s a significant drop, and on day one, assuming it happened some hours after release, is a bit sketchy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteam released new guidelines for exchange rates, and lots of games made updates at the same time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Buenasfx","CreatedById":209161,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T00:57:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1506700320\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=https://twitter.com/Buenasfx/status/1631095959210934275\u0022 style=\u0022height:514px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nerdy_Mike","CreatedById":222601,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-02T01:14:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey all,\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can confirm the price was adjusted in Mexico.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEpic Games Store purchases will be automatically refunded the difference.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteam users I am looking into if it\u0027s automatically refunded at the moment as the change just went through.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Physics Engineer","CreatedById":212132,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-03T00:41:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224249364\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022214111\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677719652\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222601\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nerdy_Mike\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, Nerdy_Mike said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey all,\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can confirm the price was adjusted in Mexico.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEpic Games Store purchases will be automatically refunded the difference.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteam users I am looking into if it\u0027s automatically refunded at the moment as the change just went through.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor me the difference was added to my Steam Wallet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}